snippet.title: Splinter Cell HD (PS3) - First 20 minutes (part 1/2)
snippet.description:
First part of the first mission (Police Station in Georgia). It's NOT a remake, the game is exactly like the original XBOX version with slightly better graphics, in HD, stereoscopic 3D (optional) and trophy support.

Part 2/2: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V1KgoW6-UDY
